| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-1244 — Recovery Inhibition (bianlian)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: bdfe7a08-5099-5eed-a40f-2f2061bbb6ef"
